metadata.description: Astroglyphs are an on-chain generative art on the Ethereum blockchain. A completely self-constrained mechanism is used for the creation and ownership of the artwork. The design of each Astroglyph will live completely on the Ethereum blockchain as part of the Astroglyphs NFT smart contract. Astroglyphs are very rare and only 12 of them have been minted.
metadata.name: Astroglyphs - On-Chain Generative Art - #1 Aries
